title: Manning of The Hour
description:
Wendi Nix, Rod Gilmore, and Tom Luginbill discuss the newest star in the Manning Family. Mack Brown and Jeff Saturday join the show. plus, Heather Dinich gives us the latest on Nick Saban and Alabama as they prepare for a show down with Georgia in Tuscaloosa.
